Package: igniteR
Title: Streamlined Firebase Authentication for R Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.1
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R: 
    person("Lauren", "Green", email = "ghouse.performance@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simplifies the integration of Firebase Authentication in R Shiny web applications. 
    This package provides a streamlined interface to Firebase's Authentication REST API, 
    offering easy-to-use functions for implementing secure user authentication, account 
    management, and user profile operations in Shiny apps. Features include email/password 
    authentication, OAuth integration, password reset capabilities, and user profile management.
License: GPL-3
